title: On Feminism (vs. 3rd Wave Feminism)
description: This is another "Old Patreon Exclusive".  By now, most of you can guess what my position is on 3rd wave feminism, but, at that time, I did receive questions about it. ;-)  https://www.patreon.com/a_bas_le_ciel/
